    {
      "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-8002-b91a-cb8d6a7c7d4b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Group formation, although essential for collaborative learning is a very difficult task. The authors use a form of graph-based modelling to identify similarity between different members. Then, the authors propose a binary integer model to solve group formation on a sample of 32 students (groups of 4). ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-8002-b91a-cb8d6a7c7d4b",
        "parent": {
